WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.430 --> 00:00:03.180
Earth

2
00:00:04.310 --> 00:00:05.620
Fire

3
00:00:07.190 --> 00:00:09.300
Air

4
00:00:11.520 --> 00:00:13.270
Water

5
00:00:15.800 --> 00:00:19.430
When I was a boy. my father. Avatar Aang

6
00:00:19.430 --> 00:00:21.780
told me the story of how he and his friends

7
00:00:21.780 --> 00:00:24.010
heroically ended the 100 year war.

8
00:00:24.010 --> 00:00:27.290
Avatar Aang and Firelord Zuko

9
00:00:27.290 --> 00:00:29.600
transformed the Fire Nation colonies

10
00:00:29.600 --> 00:00:31.570
into the United Republic of Nations

11
00:00:31.960 --> 00:00:36.510
a society where benders and
non-benders from all over the world

12
00:00:36.510 --> 00:00:40.900
would live and thrive together
in peace and harmony

13
00:00:41.610 --> 00:00:45.350
They named the capital of this
great land Republic City

14
00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:50.420
Avatar Aang accomplished many
remarkable things in his life

15
00:00:50.830 --> 00:00:54.400
but. sadly. his time in
this world came to an end

16
00:00:54.400 --> 00:00:56.680
and like the cicle of the seasons

17
00:00:56.680 --> 00:00:59.990
the cicle of the Avatar began anew

18
00:01:22.210 --> 00:01:24.950
The White Lotus has
honored my family by coming

19
00:01:25.060 --> 00:01:26.340
Thank you.

20
00:01:29.290 --> 00:01:31.370
Welcome.

21
00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:34.580
We have investigated many claims

22
00:01:34.580 --> 00:01:37.510
both here and in the Northern Tribe

23
00:01:37.710 --> 00:01:39.540
all of them turned out to be false.

24
00:01:39.540 --> 00:01:43.740
Then you should be happy to know
that your search has come to an end.

25
00:01:43.740 --> 00:01:46.040
What makes you so sure that your daughter is...

26
00:01:46.040 --> 00:01:47.040
the one?

27
00:01:48.260 --> 00:01:50.260
Korra! please come in here

28
00:01:53.520 --> 00:01:56.540
I'm the Avatar!
You gotta deal with it!

29
00:02:40.430 --> 00:02:41.860
She's strong.

30
00:02:41.860 --> 00:02:43.930
But she lacks restraint.

31
00:03:06.650 --> 00:03:08.660
Hey! Why all the doom and gloom. people?

32
00:03:08.660 --> 00:03:10.360
We should be celebrating!

33
00:03:10.360 --> 00:03:12.550
Three elements down. one to go!

34
00:03:12.550 --> 00:03:15.500
You are getting ahead of yourself as usual. Korrra.

35
00:03:15.500 --> 00:03:18.240
We haven't decided if you
passed your fire bending test yet.

36
00:03:18.240 --> 00:03:21.400
Ever since you were a little girl
you excelled at the fisical side of bending

37
00:03:21.400 --> 00:03:24.690
but completely ignored the spiritual side.

38
00:03:24.690 --> 00:03:27.440
The Avatar must master both.

39
00:03:27.440 --> 00:03:30.080
I haven't ignored it.
it just hasn't come as easy to me.

40
00:03:30.080 --> 00:03:33.840
But that's why I should start
training with Tenzin immediately

41
00:03:34.160 --> 00:03:35.620
he's "Mister Spiritual".

42
00:03:35.620 --> 00:03:37.930
Do you believe she's ready.
Master Katara?

43
00:03:37.970 --> 00:03:39.330
Yes.

44
00:03:39.530 --> 00:03:41.690
If anyone can teach her what she has to learn.

45
00:03:41.690 --> 00:03:43.280
it's Tenzin.

46
00:03:43.280 --> 00:03:44.870
Very well. Korra.

47
00:03:44.870 --> 00:03:47.770
It's time for you to begin your airbending training

48
00:03:47.770 --> 00:03:50.070
Yes! Finally!

49
00:03:52.410 --> 00:03:53.820
I mean... ahem!

50
00:03:53.820 --> 00:03:56.730
Thank you all for believing in me.

51
00:04:04.110 --> 00:04:05.570
Naga! You should have seen it.

52
00:04:05.570 --> 00:04:08.890
I kicked some firebending butt. and I passed!

53
00:04:08.890 --> 00:04:11.530
Tenzin will be here in a few days.

54
00:04:20.180 --> 00:04:22.670
Just taking Naga out for a stroll.

55
00:04:24.220 --> 00:04:26.820
Don't worry. we're not going far.

56
00:04:39.050 --> 00:04:41.140
Naga. go!

57
00:04:51.660 --> 00:04:54.510
Are we there yet? Are we
there yet? Are we there yet?

58
00:04:54.510 --> 00:04:57.010
It looks like we're there. I know cause it's very familiar.

59
00:04:57.010 --> 00:04:58.520
Are we here yet? Are we there yet?
Ooooh please tell me we're here!

60
00:04:58.630 --> 00:04:59.550
Yes. Ikki.

61
00:04:59.550 --> 00:05:03.040
As I've been telling you for the last 15 minutes

62
00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:06.020
we are. FINALLY. here.

63
00:05:08.520 --> 00:05:09.760
Hello. Mother.

64
00:05:09.760 --> 00:05:12.260
I can't tell you how happy I am to see you.

65
00:05:12.260 --> 00:05:14.410
Please. help me.

66
00:05:15.670 --> 00:05:17.740
Unhand me. strange woman!

67
00:05:17.740 --> 00:05:19.320
That's your grandmother. Milo.

68
00:05:23.460 --> 00:05:25.990
It's so good to see all of you.

69
00:05:25.990 --> 00:05:29.220
Gran Gran. I've been reading all about your old adventures.

70
00:05:29.220 --> 00:05:30.930
and I've been dying to ask you

71
00:05:30.970 --> 00:05:32.830
What happened to Zuko's mom?

72
00:05:32.830 --> 00:05:35.520
Well. Jinora. it's an incredible tale.

73
00:05:35.520 --> 00:05:38.320
Gran Gran. you look old. How old are you?

74
00:05:38.320 --> 00:05:41.780
And why is it so cold in the South Pole?
Can we make a campfire and and all huddle around it

75
00:05:41.780 --> 00:05:44.000
and tell scary stories an make snowmen?

76
00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:46.680
And then can you make the snowmen
move with Waterbending and chase us?

77
00:05:46.970 --> 00:05:49.130
Wouldn't that be fun? Huh? Wouldn't it?

78
00:05:49.520 --> 00:05:51.280
Pema. let me help you.

79
00:05:51.280 --> 00:05:52.800
Careful now. Careful.

80
00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:54.570
Stop doting on me.

81
00:05:54.570 --> 00:05:55.530
I'm not helpless

82
00:05:55.530 --> 00:05:57.500
I'm just pregnant!

83
00:06:00.370 --> 00:06:02.190
The baby is strong.

84
00:06:02.190 --> 00:06:04.820
I see another airbender in your future.

85
00:06:05.560 --> 00:06:08.190
All I want is one child like me!

86
00:06:08.190 --> 00:06:11.800
A nice non-bender who doesn't blast
wind at my face every five seconds.

87
00:06:11.800 --> 00:06:14.050
Mommy. look!

88
00:06:14.050 --> 00:06:15.780
I'm a snowbender!

89
00:06:18.420 --> 00:06:21.000
Were Tenzin and his siblings this crazy

90
00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:22.120
when they were kids?

91
00:06:22.550 --> 00:06:24.040
Kaya and Boomy certainly were

92
00:06:24.040 --> 00:06:26.530
but Tenzin has always been...

93
00:06:26.570 --> 00:06:27.500
rather serious.

94
00:06:27.840 --> 00:06:29.750
Mother... please.

95
00:06:32.740 --> 00:06:33.900
Korra?

96
00:06:35.310 --> 00:06:37.350
Look at you. so big and strong.

97
00:06:37.670 --> 00:06:39.440
You've grown into quite the young Avatar.

98
00:06:39.440 --> 00:06:42.240
Master Tenzin. I'm so glad you're here.

99
00:06:42.240 --> 00:06:43.610
I can't wait to get started.

100
00:06:43.610 --> 00:06:45.930
Yes.. well...

101
00:06:46.630 --> 00:06:49.050
You're going to have to
tell her sooner or later.

102
00:06:49.050 --> 00:06:50.110
Tell me what?

103
00:06:51.010 --> 00:06:52.510
You're not staying. are you?

104
00:06:54.100 --> 00:06:55.270
I'm afraid not.

105
00:06:55.580 --> 00:06:57.170
We're only visiting for the night.

106
00:06:57.170 --> 00:06:59.980
Then. I have to return to Republic City.

107
00:06:59.980 --> 00:07:02.820
But... you're suposed to move here!

108
00:07:03.570 --> 00:07:05.000
You're suposed to teach me!

109
00:07:05.000 --> 00:07:06.810
I'm sorry. Korra.

110
00:07:07.070 --> 00:07:09.390
Your airbending training
is going to have to wait.

111
00:07:13.610 --> 00:07:16.970
Well. how long until you're
ready to tech me airbending?

112
00:07:16.970 --> 00:07:18.210
A week? A month?

113
00:07:18.210 --> 00:07:20.310
It could be much longer.

114
00:07:20.310 --> 00:07:21.670
I don't understand.

115
00:07:21.670 --> 00:07:23.340
Why are you making me wait?

116
00:07:23.340 --> 00:07:25.550
I have a responsibility to Republic City.

117
00:07:25.550 --> 00:07:27.170
I'm one of it's leaders.

118
00:07:27.170 --> 00:07:29.860
and the situation there is very unstable right now.

119
00:07:29.860 --> 00:07:33.150
But you also have a responsibility to teach me.

120
00:07:33.150 --> 00:07:36.420
Believe me! I would be happy
to find another airbending master.

121
00:07:36.530 --> 00:07:37.970
But you are the only one.

122
00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:39.790
We're stuck with each other.

123
00:07:39.790 --> 00:07:41.500
I wish there were another way

124
00:07:41.500 --> 00:07:43.090
Wait! there is!

125
00:07:43.090 --> 00:07:46.900
If you can't stay here. then
I'll go back to Republic City with you!

126
00:07:46.900 --> 00:07:48.270
It's perfect!

127
00:07:48.530 --> 00:07:49.900
Absolutely not.

128
00:07:49.900 --> 00:07:51.710
The city is far too dangerous!

129
00:07:51.710 --> 00:07:54.830
Avatar Aang tasked us with keeping you safe

130
00:07:54.830 --> 00:07:56.640
while you master the four elements!

131
00:07:56.640 --> 00:07:58.360
I get that. but

132
00:07:58.360 --> 00:08:00.460
I don't think keeping me locked up
in this compound like a prisoner

133
00:08:00.460 --> 00:08:02.270
is what he had in mind.

134
00:08:02.270 --> 00:08:04.410
I know this is difficult to accept

135
00:08:04.410 --> 00:08:07.270
but it's not the right time
for you to come to the city.

136
00:08:07.270 --> 00:08:08.160
Whatever!

137
00:08:13.930 --> 00:08:15.250
Goodbye. Gran Gran!

138
00:08:47.740 --> 00:08:49.980
Nice night for an escape. isn't it?

139
00:08:52.140 --> 00:08:53.140
I have to leave.

140
00:08:53.140 --> 00:08:55.700
I have to find my own path as the Avatar.

141
00:08:55.700 --> 00:08:58.890
I know you do.

142
00:09:00.740 --> 00:09:02.130
Aang's time has passed.

143
00:09:02.130 --> 00:09:05.940
My brother and many of my friends are gone.

144
00:09:05.940 --> 00:09:09.010
It's time for you and your generation

145
00:09:09.010 --> 00:09:11.680
to take over the responsibility of keeping peace

146
00:09:11.680 --> 00:09:13.660
and balance in the world

147
00:09:13.660 --> 00:09:17.320
and I think you're going to be a great Avatar.

148
00:09:18.150 --> 00:09:20.280
Thank you.

149
00:09:20.430 --> 00:09:21.860
Goodbye. Korra.

150
00:09:34.360 --> 00:09:36.060
Mom. Dad...

151
00:09:37.020 --> 00:09:38.370
I'll miss you.

152
00:09:38.370 --> 00:09:41.010
We love you so much.

153
00:10:17.410 --> 00:10:18.250
Naga! we're here!

154
00:10:28.960 --> 00:10:30.430
Thanks for the ride!

155
00:10:39.310 --> 00:10:40.080
Wow!

156
00:10:40.080 --> 00:10:42.180
Look at this place!

157
00:10:42.180 --> 00:10:45.060
I've never seen no many Satomobiles!

158
00:10:55.550 --> 00:10:57.170
Airtemple Island

159
00:10:57.170 --> 00:10:59.100
That's were Tenzin is.

160
00:10:59.100 --> 00:11:00.840
Ready for a little swim. girl?

161
00:11:02.390 --> 00:11:04.250
Okay. okay!

162
00:11:04.250 --> 00:11:06.480
Food first. then Airtemple.

163
00:11:07.340 --> 00:11:09.730
Watch it. Naga! Look out!

164
00:11:15.780 --> 00:11:16.480
Excuse us!

165
00:11:16.480 --> 00:11:17.480
Coming through!

166
00:11:17.480 --> 00:11:18.130
Heads up!

167
00:11:18.130 --> 00:11:19.160
Sorry!

168
00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:29.400
Naga. wait.

169
00:11:32.690 --> 00:11:34.380
We'll take one of everything. please.

170
00:11:34.380 --> 00:11:35.970
That'll be 20 Yuans.

171
00:11:35.970 --> 00:11:39.500
Err... I don't have any money.

172
00:11:39.500 --> 00:11:41.090
Then what good are you to me!

173
00:11:43.960 --> 00:11:46.220
Don't worry. girl.
The city is huge!

174
00:11:46.220 --> 00:11:47.780
I bet we can find a place

175
00:11:47.780 --> 00:11:49.920
to rustle up something to eat.

176
00:12:05.330 --> 00:12:06.330
Uh... say!

177
00:12:06.590 --> 00:12:09.040
Think I can get one of them tasty smelling fishies?

178
00:12:09.040 --> 00:12:11.340
Oh! err... Yeah. sure!

179
00:12:14.300 --> 00:12:12.340
So

180
00:12:16.400 --> 00:12:18.810
You... live in that bush?

181
00:12:18.810 --> 00:12:21.720
Yes! Presently that is what I do call "home"

182
00:12:22.030 --> 00:12:24.890
Took me a while to procure a bush that beauty.

183
00:12:24.890 --> 00:12:28.340
This park is quite popular with all the vagabonds.

184
00:12:28.500 --> 00:12:31.080
So there are a lot of you out here?

185
00:12:31.420 --> 00:12:34.110
I thought everyone in this city was living it up?

186
00:12:36.080 --> 00:12:37.970
You got a lot to learn newcomer.

187
00:12:37.970 --> 00:12:39.770
Welcome to Republic City.

188
00:12:40.230 --> 00:12:42.260
Hey you!

189
00:12:42.310 --> 00:12:44.760
Stop! You can't fish here!

190
00:12:45.360 --> 00:12:46.700
You best skedaddle!

191
00:12:58.350 --> 00:13:01.190
Are you tired of living under the tyranny of benders?

192
00:13:01.560 --> 00:13:03.830
Then join the Equalists!

193
00:13:03.830 --> 00:13:07.580
For too long the bending elite of this city have forced

194
00:13:07.580 --> 00:13:10.500
nonbenders to live as lower class citizens!

195
00:13:10.900 --> 00:13:11.900
Join Amon!

196
00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:13.910
And together we will tear down

197
00:13:13.910 --> 00:13:15.720
the bending establishment!

198
00:13:15.720 --> 00:13:16.710
What are you talking about?

199
00:13:16.710 --> 00:13:18.690
Bending is the coolest thing in the world!

200
00:13:18.690 --> 00:13:20.090
Oh yeah?

201
00:13:20.090 --> 00:13:21.180
Let me guess

202
00:13:21.240 --> 00:13:22.960
you're a bender.

203
00:13:22.960 --> 00:13:23.960
Yeah. I am.

204
00:13:24.380 --> 00:13:28.780
Then I bet you'd love to just knock me off
this platform with some Waterbending huh?

205
00:13:28.780 --> 00:13:30.750
I'm seriously thinking about it.

206
00:13:30.750 --> 00:13:33.400
This is what's wrong with the City!

207
00:13:33.400 --> 00:13:37.230
Benders like this girl only use
their powers to oppress us!

208
00:13:39.340 --> 00:13:40.560
What?!

209
00:13:40.560 --> 00:13:42.170
I'm not oppressing anyone!

210
00:13:42.170 --> 00:13:43.520
You...

211
00:13:43.520 --> 00:13:44.970
You're oppressing yourselves!

212
00:13:45.500 --> 00:13:47.360
That didn't even make sense!

213
00:13:53.480 --> 00:13:55.690
Excuse me. I think I'm lost.

214
00:13:55.690 --> 00:13:57.560
How do I get to Air Temple Island from here?

215
00:13:57.560 --> 00:14:00.060
Just head down this street

216
00:14:01.230 --> 00:14:03.520
You should get moving young lady.

217
00:14:03.520 --> 00:14:04.830
It isn't safe!

218
00:14:07.300 --> 00:14:09.860
Mr. Chung.

219
00:14:09.860 --> 00:14:12.560
please tell met that you have my money

220
00:14:12.560 --> 00:14:16.590
or else I can't guarantee that
I can protect your fine establishment.

221
00:14:16.590 --> 00:14:18.900
I'm sorry! Business has been slow!

222
00:14:18.900 --> 00:14:21.140
Please! Take one of my phonographs.

223
00:14:23.730 --> 00:14:27.030
My friend here is not a music lover.

224
00:14:27.030 --> 00:14:29.270
Give me the money or else

225
00:14:29.270 --> 00:14:30.710
Or else what. hoodlum?

226
00:14:40.320 --> 00:14:42.840
Since you're obviously fresh off the boat.

227
00:14:42.840 --> 00:14:45.120
let me explain a couple things.

228
00:14:45.120 --> 00:14:48.180
You're in Triple Threat Triad territory

229
00:14:48.580 --> 00:14:51.670
and we're about to put you in the hospital.

230
00:14:51.670 --> 00:14:54.040
You're the only ones who are gonna need a hospital.

231
00:14:54.040 --> 00:14:56.960
And for your sake I hope there's one near by.

232
00:14:56.960 --> 00:14:58.700
Who do you think you are?

233
00:14:58.700 --> 00:15:00.620
Why don't you come and find out?

234
00:15:12.830 --> 00:15:15.630
- What just happened?
- Did she just Earthbend?

235
00:15:25.590 --> 00:15:27.780
Can she Firebend too?

236
00:15:27.780 --> 00:15:29.150
Could she be…?

237
00:15:34.810 --> 00:15:37.520
Got an idea about who I am now?

238
00:15:37.530 --> 00:15:38.530
Chumps

239
00:15:43.080 --> 00:15:43.850
Come on!

240
00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:47.970
You're not getting away!

241
00:16:03.070 --> 00:16:04.190
Police! Freeze where you are!

242
00:16:10.840 --> 00:16:12.300
Cool. Metalbenders…

243
00:16:19.770 --> 00:16:22.070
I caught the bad guys for you officers.

244
00:16:22.070 --> 00:16:23.560
Arrest them!

245
00:16:28.430 --> 00:16:30.340
You're under arrest too.

246
00:16:34.250 --> 00:16:35.830
What do you mean I'm under arrest?

247
00:16:35.830 --> 00:16:38.970
Those are the bad guys over there!
They were smashing up a shop.

248
00:16:38.970 --> 00:16:41.820
From the looks of it. you smashed up a lot more than that.

249
00:16:42.730 --> 00:16:44.570
Wait! You can't arrest me!

250
00:16:44.570 --> 00:16:45.570
Let me explain!

251
00:16:45.630 --> 00:16:47.620
You can explain yourself all you like

252
00:16:47.620 --> 00:16:48.750
down at headquarters.

253
00:17:59.670 --> 00:18:01.350
Let's see…

254
00:18:01.350 --> 00:18:05.800
Multiple counts of destruction of private and city property

255
00:18:05.800 --> 00:18:08.340
not to mention resisting arrest.

256
00:18:08.340 --> 00:18:11.360
You're in a whole mess of trouble young lady.

257
00:18:11.360 --> 00:18:14.000
But they were some thugs
threatening a helpless shopkeeper and I

258
00:18:14.000 --> 00:18:17.990
Can it! You should have called the police and stayed out of the way.

259
00:18:18.010 --> 00:18:20.160
But I couldn't just sit by and do nothing.

260
00:18:20.160 --> 00:18:22.200
It's my duty to help people.

261
00:18:22.200 --> 00:18:24.510
See. I'm the Avatar.

262
00:18:25.540 --> 00:18:27.630
Oh. I am well aware of who you are.

263
00:18:27.630 --> 00:18:31.000
And your Avatar title might impress some people

264
00:18:31.000 --> 00:18:32.360
but not me.

265
00:18:33.030 --> 00:18:34.600
All right. fine.

266
00:18:34.600 --> 00:18:36.880
Then I want to talk to whoever's in charge.

267
00:18:36.880 --> 00:18:38.350
You're talking to her.

268
00:18:38.350 --> 00:18:40.090
I'm Chief Bei Fong.

269
00:18:40.090 --> 00:18:42.030
Wait…Bei Fong

270
00:18:42.030 --> 00:18:43.860
Lin Bei Fong?

271
00:18:43.860 --> 00:18:45.030
You're Toph's daughter!

272
00:18:45.030 --> 00:18:48.060
- What of it?
- Well then why are you treating me like a criminal?

273
00:18:48.060 --> 00:18:50.360
Avatar Aang and your mother were friends.

274
00:18:50.460 --> 00:18:52.300
they saved the world together.

275
00:18:52.300 --> 00:18:53.530
That's ancient history.

276
00:18:53.830 --> 00:18:56.900
And it's got diddlysquat to do
with the mess you're in right now.

277
00:18:57.230 --> 00:19:01.770
You can't just waltz in here and dole out
vigilante justice like you own the place.

278
00:19:01.770 --> 00:19:02.500
Chief. Councilman Tenzin is here.
You can't just waltz in here and dole out
vigilante justice like you own the place.

279
00:19:02.500 --> 00:19:06.100
Chief. Councilman Tenzin is here.

280
00:19:06.100 --> 00:19:07.380
Let him in.

281
00:19:10.680 --> 00:19:13.090
Tenzin…sorry.

282
00:19:13.440 --> 00:19:16.200
I got a little side tracked
on my way to see you…

283
00:19:18.650 --> 00:19:21.840
Lin you are looking radiant as usual.

284
00:19:21.840 --> 00:19:23.500
Cut the garbage. Tenzin.

285
00:19:23.500 --> 00:19:25.550
Why is the Avatar in Republic City?

286
00:19:25.550 --> 00:19:29.040
I thought you were supposed to be
moving down to the South Pole to train her.

287
00:19:29.040 --> 00:19:31.500
My relocation has been delayed.

288
00:19:31.500 --> 00:19:36.340
The Avatar. on the other hand. will be
heading back to the South Pole immediately

289
00:19:36.340 --> 00:19:38.770
where she will stay put.

290
00:19:38.770 --> 00:19:43.080
- But—
- If you would be so kind as
to drop the charges against Korra

291
00:19:43.080 --> 00:19:46.930
I will take full responsibility for today's events

292
00:19:46.930 --> 00:19:49.080
and cover all the damages.

293
00:19:52.390 --> 00:19:55.090
Fine. get her out of my city.

294
00:19:55.140 --> 00:19:57.080
Always a pleasure Lin.

295
00:19:57.080 --> 00:19:58.430
Let's go Korra.

296
00:20:07.750 --> 00:20:09.140
Tenzin please

297
00:20:09.140 --> 00:20:10.610
don't send me back home.

298
00:20:10.610 --> 00:20:14.460
You blatantly disobeyed my wishes
and the Order of the White Lotus.

299
00:20:14.490 --> 00:20:16.780
Katara agreed with me that I should come.

300
00:20:16.780 --> 00:20:19.310
She said my destiny is in Republic City.

301
00:20:19.600 --> 00:20:21.180
Don't bring my mother into this!

302
00:20:21.180 --> 00:20:24.530
Look. I can't wait any
longer to finish my training.

303
00:20:24.530 --> 00:20:28.420
Being cooped up and hidden away from the world
isn't helping me become a better Avatar.

304
00:20:28.420 --> 00:20:31.190
I saw a lot of the city today

305
00:20:31.330 --> 00:20:33.140
and it's totally out of whack.

306
00:20:33.140 --> 00:20:35.560
I understand now why you need to stay.

307
00:20:35.560 --> 00:20:37.580
Republic City does need you

308
00:20:37.580 --> 00:20:39.270
but it needs me too.

309
00:20:39.270 --> 00:20:40.960
You...

310
00:20:43.620 --> 00:20:46.390
Is this your polar bear-dog. miss?

311
00:21:15.330 --> 00:21:18.110
Korra!

312
00:21:19.530 --> 00:21:21.450
Are you coming to live with us on the island?

313
00:21:21.710 --> 00:21:24.500
No. I'm sorry Ikki.

314
00:21:24.500 --> 00:21:25.630
I have to go home now.

315
00:21:32.110 --> 00:21:33.580
Wait.

316
00:21:34.150 --> 00:21:36.970
I have done my best to guide Republic City

317
00:21:36.970 --> 00:21:38.910
towards the dream my father had for it.

318
00:21:38.910 --> 00:21:42.650
But you're right. it has fallen
out of balance since he passed.

319
00:21:42.650 --> 00:21:46.270
I thought I should put off your training
in order to uphold hid legacy.

320
00:21:46.270 --> 00:21:49.060
But you are his legacy.

321
00:21:49.060 --> 00:21:52.560
You may stay and train Airbending here with me.

322
00:21:52.560 --> 00:21:55.460
Republic City needs it's Avatar once again.

323
00:21:55.460 --> 00:21:58.290
Yes! Thank you! You're the best!

324
00:22:14.890 --> 00:22:16.140
Hello…

325
00:22:16.470 --> 00:22:18.170
I'm Korra.

326
00:22:18.170 --> 00:22:20.520
your new Avatar.

327
00:22:20.520 --> 00:22:22.980
Does this mean you've
moved to Republic City?

328
00:22:22.980 --> 00:22:25.600
Were you trying to send a message
to the Triads yesterday?

329
00:22:25.600 --> 00:22:29.090
Will you be fighting crime or the
anti-bending revolution or both?

330
00:22:29.310 --> 00:22:31.590
Will you be working with
Chief Bei Fong and the police?

331
00:22:31.590 --> 00:22:34.450
Uhh…yes I am definitely here to stay

332
00:22:34.450 --> 00:22:38.700
but honestly…I don't exactly have a plan yet…

333
00:22:38.700 --> 00:22:40.970
See I'm still in training but…

334
00:22:40.970 --> 00:22:42.130
Look.

335
00:22:42.130 --> 00:22:45.130
all I know is Avatar Aang meant for this city

336
00:22:45.130 --> 00:22:48.380
to be the center of peace and balance in the world

337
00:22:48.380 --> 00:22:49.810
and

338
00:22:49.810 --> 00:22:52.700
I believe we can make his dream a reality.

339
00:22:52.700 --> 00:22:55.420
I look forward to serving you!

340
00:22:55.420 --> 00:22:58.440
I'm so happy to be here!

341
00:22:58.730 --> 00:23:00.270
Than you Republic City!

342
00:23:00.270 --> 00:23:02.660
All right that's all the questions the Av—

343
00:23:02.660 --> 00:23:05.670
Amon. how do you want to handle this?

344
00:23:05.670 --> 00:23:08.890
So. the Avatar has arrived early.

345
00:23:08.890 --> 00:23:11.840
It looks like we'll have
to accelerate our plans.

346
00:23:31.860 --> 00:23:36.530
"And in the final round the Buzzard Wasps
won with a decisive knockout."

347
00:23:36.530 --> 00:23:38.610
What do you say we go to the arena tonight?

348
00:23:38.610 --> 00:23:40.150
Catch a few Pro-Bending matches?

349
00:23:40.150 --> 00:23:44.260
That sport is a mockery of the
noble tradition of bending.

350
00:23:44.260 --> 00:23:46.150
Come on Tenzin!

351
00:23:46.150 --> 00:23:48.620
I dreamed about seeing a
Pro-Bending match since I was a kid

352
00:23:48.620 --> 00:23:50.720
and now I'm just a ferry ride
away from the arena.

353
00:23:50.720 --> 00:23:52.910
Korra. you're not here to watch that drivel.

354
00:23:52.910 --> 00:23:54.930
You're here to finish your Avatar training.

355
00:23:54.930 --> 00:23:58.320
so for the time being
I want you to remain on the island.

356
00:23:58.320 --> 00:24:00.320
Is that why you're keeping the
White Lotus sentries around

357
00:24:00.320 --> 00:24:02.550
to watch my every move?

358
00:24:02.550 --> 00:24:04.140
Yes. In order to learn Airbending

359
00:24:04.140 --> 00:24:06.720
I believe you require a
calm. quiet environment

360
00:24:06.720 --> 00:24:08.670
free from any distractions.

361
00:24:08.670 --> 00:24:09.970
Alright.

362
00:24:09.970 --> 00:24:11.240
You're the master.

363
00:24:19.040 --> 00:24:20.080
So

364
00:24:20.080 --> 00:24:23.560
my mother informed me you've
never been able to Airbend before.

365
00:24:25.090 --> 00:24:27.090
Yeah but I don't know why.

366
00:24:27.090 --> 00:24:29.160
The other elements came SO easily to me

367
00:24:29.160 --> 00:24:31.750
but every single time I've tried Airbending

368
00:24:32.380 --> 00:24:33.510
nothing.

369
00:24:33.510 --> 00:24:36.240
That's perfectly all right.
We just need to be patient.

370
00:24:36.240 --> 00:24:37.240
Often the element that's most
difficult for the Avatar to master

371
00:24:39.890 --> 00:24:42.190
is the one most opposite
to the Avatar's personality.

372
00:24:42.230 --> 00:24:44.260
For Aang it was Earthbending.

373
00:24:44.260 --> 00:24:47.550
Yeah well. I'm about as opposite
an Airbender as you can get.

374
00:24:47.950 --> 00:24:49.900
Let's begin your first lesson.

375
00:24:51.620 --> 00:24:55.360
Korra's gonna Airbend!
Korra's gonna Airbend!

376
00:24:55.360 --> 00:24:57.260
What is that contraption.

377
00:24:57.260 --> 00:24:59.040
A time-honored tool

378
00:24:59.040 --> 00:25:01.930
that teaches the most
fundamental aspect of Airbending.

379
00:25:01.930 --> 00:25:04.470
Jinora would you like
to explain this exercise.

380
00:25:04.480 --> 00:25:06.930
The goal is to weave your
way through the gates

381
00:25:06.930 --> 00:25:08.910
and make it to the other side
without touching them.

382
00:25:10.070 --> 00:25:11.040
Seems easy enough.

383
00:25:11.370 --> 00:25:13.980
Jinora forgot to say you have to make
it through while the gates are spinning.

384
00:25:23.180 --> 00:25:26.380
The key is to be like the leaf.

385
00:25:27.910 --> 00:25:29.880
Flow

386
00:25:29.880 --> 00:25:31.460
with the movement of the gates.

387
00:25:32.380 --> 00:25:34.750
Jinora will demonstrate.

388
00:25:36.810 --> 00:25:39.430
Airbending is all about spiral movements.

389
00:25:39.430 --> 00:25:40.960
When you meet resistance

390
00:25:40.960 --> 00:25:44.250
you must be able to switch direction
at a moment's notice.

391
00:25:51.800 --> 00:25:53.030
Let's do this.

392
00:26:09.820 --> 00:26:11.550
Don't force your way through!

393
00:26:11.550 --> 00:26:14.420
Dance! Dance like the wind!

394
00:26:14.420 --> 00:26:17.220
Be the leaf!

395
00:26:28.890 --> 00:26:30.000
Airbend!

396
00:26:32.770 --> 00:26:34.430
What is wrong with me?

397
00:26:34.430 --> 00:26:36.260
Airbend!

398
00:26:42.920 --> 00:26:45.650
Maybe I'm just not cut out to be an Airbender.
huh. Naga?

399
00:26:45.650 --> 00:26:47.900
Ladies and gentlemen! I'm coming to you live

400
00:26:47.900 --> 00:26:50.110
from Republic City's Pro-Bending arena

401
00:26:50.110 --> 00:26:52.120
where tonight the best in the world

402
00:26:52.120 --> 00:26:56.050
continue their quest for a spot in
the upcoming championship tournament.

403
00:26:56.050 --> 00:26:58.200
Grab your snacks and grab your kids

404
00:26:58.200 --> 00:27:01.140
because this next match is gonna be a doozy!

405
00:27:01.140 --> 00:27:03.450
This Mako's got moxy!

406
00:27:03.450 --> 00:27:05.500
He fires to quick shots.

407
00:27:05.500 --> 00:27:07.810
Yomo is hammered back to zone 3.

408
00:27:07.810 --> 00:27:10.040
Clock is winding down. can Yomo hold on?

409
00:27:10.040 --> 00:27:11.750
He's teetering on the edge of the ring now.

410
00:27:11.750 --> 00:27:15.000
The Fire Ferrets—

411
00:27:17.250 --> 00:27:18.250
Korra come down here. please.

412
00:27:21.540 --> 00:27:22.960
You shut it off at the best part!

413
00:27:22.960 --> 00:27:24.920
I thought I made myself clear.

414
00:27:24.920 --> 00:27:28.220
I don't want you listening to this
distracting nonsense

415
00:27:28.220 --> 00:27:29.800
But it's their radio.

416
00:27:29.800 --> 00:27:34.890
And technically you said I couldn't watch a match.
You said nothing about listening to one.

417
00:27:34.890 --> 00:27:35.800
You...-

418
00:27:35.800 --> 00:27:37.670
you know what I meant.

419
00:27:37.670 --> 00:27:39.110
Anyway shouldn't you—

420
00:27:39.110 --> 00:27:40.110
shouldn't you be in bed by now!

421
00:27:58.560 --> 00:28:00.880
I think I'm doing it wrong.

422
00:28:00.880 --> 00:28:02.360
There's nothing to do.

423
00:28:02.360 --> 00:28:04.850
Let your mind and your spirit be free

424
00:28:04.850 --> 00:28:07.090
for Air is the element of freedom.

425
00:28:09.720 --> 00:28:11.520
Is something funny?

426
00:28:11.520 --> 00:28:15.790
Yeah. you're telling me to embrace freedom
and yet you won't even let me listen to the radio.

427
00:28:16.180 --> 00:28:18.190
And forget about leaving this island.

428
00:28:18.190 --> 00:28:21.330
Please Korra. Look at Meelo.

429
00:28:21.330 --> 00:28:23.080
He's able to meditate peacefully.

430
00:28:26.140 --> 00:28:27.980
He's able to meditate peacefully.

431
00:28:27.980 --> 00:28:28.730
What?

432
00:28:28.730 --> 00:28:31.690
Well. at least he has the relaxing part down.

433
00:28:31.690 --> 00:28:32.760
Whatever.

434
00:28:32.760 --> 00:28:34.980
none of this Airbending stuff
makes any sense to me.

435
00:28:34.980 --> 00:28:36.480
I know you're frustrated

436
00:28:36.480 --> 00:28:38.800
but these teachings will sink in over time

437
00:28:38.800 --> 00:28:40.180
then one day

438
00:28:40.180 --> 00:28:41.950
they'll just click.

439
00:28:43.880 --> 00:28:46.980
Yeah it's not sinking in.

440
00:28:46.980 --> 00:28:48.960
I'm gonna go get a
glass of leechee juice.

441
00:28:48.960 --> 00:28:49.970
Korra!

442
00:28:50.480 --> 00:28:51.460
The meditation's not over yet!

443
00:28:51.460 --> 00:28:54.000
Daddy can I have
some leechee juice too?

444
00:28:54.000 --> 00:28:55.200
No.

445
00:30:03.010 --> 00:30:04.060
Hey!

446
00:30:04.060 --> 00:30:05.750
What are you doing in my gym?

447
00:30:05.750 --> 00:30:08.770
I was just looking for a bathroom
and I got lost.

448
00:30:08.770 --> 00:30:11.710
Oh the old "I had to pee excuse".

449
00:30:11.710 --> 00:30:14.940
You know. I'm sick and tired of
you kids sneaking in without paying.

450
00:30:14.940 --> 00:30:16.300
I'm taking you to security.

451
00:30:16.300 --> 00:30:18.200
- No wait...!
- There you are!

452
00:30:18.200 --> 00:30:20.280
I've been looking everywhere for you.

453
00:30:20.280 --> 00:30:23.400
It's alright Toza. she's with me.

454
00:30:23.400 --> 00:30:24.530
Yeah. I'm with him.

455
00:30:24.530 --> 00:30:25.530
So you see. we're together.

456
00:30:26.070 --> 00:30:27.470
Well not "together together".

457
00:30:27.470 --> 00:30:30.510
more like friends.
- Right friends. no. no I didn't mean to imply…

458
00:30:30.510 --> 00:30:31.510
Oh you implied it.

459
00:30:31.520 --> 00:30:33.210
I don't care what you are!

460
00:30:33.210 --> 00:30:34.280
I've got work to do.

461
00:30:36.010 --> 00:30:38.290
Right this way miss.

462
00:30:38.290 --> 00:30:40.170
Why thank you sir.

463
00:30:40.590 --> 00:30:42.250
Seriously thanks.

464
00:30:44.300 --> 00:30:45.950
What do you think?

465
00:30:46.560 --> 00:30:48.080
Best seats in the house. huh?

466
00:30:48.080 --> 00:30:49.630
Whoa…

467
00:30:49.630 --> 00:30:51.610
Unbelievable!

468
00:30:51.610 --> 00:30:55.010
this place is even more amazing
than I imagined.

469
00:30:55.010 --> 00:30:56.790
Name's Bolin. by the way.

470
00:30:56.790 --> 00:30:58.080
Korra

471
00:30:58.080 --> 00:31:01.000
- Pssst. Bolin!
- Yeah?

472
00:31:01.000 --> 00:31:05.460
I told you. you have to stop bringing
your crazy fangirls in here before the matches.

473
00:31:05.460 --> 00:31:07.090
Get her out of here.

474
00:31:07.090 --> 00:31:09.400
Ah come on Mako!

475
00:31:09.400 --> 00:31:12.470
I kinda promised her she could stay

476
00:31:12.470 --> 00:31:15.460
but man I got a good feeling.
There's something special about her

477
00:31:15.460 --> 00:31:18.660
I know it. Come here. I want you
to meet my brother

478
00:31:18.660 --> 00:31:20.230
Mako

479
00:31:20.230 --> 00:31:21.230
Mako?

480
00:31:21.520 --> 00:31:22.520
Wow I heard you play on the radio.

481
00:31:23.240 --> 00:31:24.580
Come on Bolin we're up.

482
00:31:24.580 --> 00:31:27.310
Or I could meet him later.

483
00:31:27.310 --> 00:31:28.710
Yeah. Sorry about that.

484
00:31:28.710 --> 00:31:31.590
My brother gets real focused before a match.

485
00:31:31.590 --> 00:31:33.770
Well I gotta go.

486
00:31:33.770 --> 00:31:35.250
Wish me luck.

487
00:31:35.250 --> 00:31:36.770
Not that I'll need it.

488
00:31:36.770 --> 00:31:38.790
Good luck!

489
00:31:38.790 --> 00:31:40.300
Knock 'em out!

490
00:31:46.020 --> 00:31:50.440
Introducing the Fire Ferrets!

491
00:31:50.690 --> 00:31:52.860
Ahhhh!! I love you Bolin.

492
00:31:52.860 --> 00:31:55.490
The rookie Ferrets came out of nowhere

493
00:31:55.490 --> 00:31:58.050
and have made it further
than anyone expected this season.

494
00:31:58.050 --> 00:32:01.050
But tonight they face
their toughest test yet folks.

495
00:32:04.370 --> 00:32:05.250
And they're off.

496
00:32:06.680 --> 00:32:07.930
The two teams waste no time

497
00:32:07.930 --> 00:32:10.250
trying to blast each other out of zone 1.

498
00:32:12.110 --> 00:32:14.600
Hasook is the first to feel
the heat of the Tigerdilloes.

499
00:32:14.600 --> 00:32:17.760
he tries to return the favor
but they're too fast for him.

500
00:32:17.760 --> 00:32:20.890
While Mako showcases his trademark
cool under fire style.

501
00:32:24.740 --> 00:32:28.010
And the Tigerdilloes score
with a walloping one-two combo.

502
00:32:28.010 --> 00:32:32.040
Can their teammate…

503
00:32:35.520 --> 00:32:36.590
Guess not.

504
00:32:36.590 --> 00:32:37.880
Mako's over the line.

505
00:32:37.880 --> 00:32:41.310
The Tigerdilloes get the green line
and advance into Ferret territory.

506
00:32:41.310 --> 00:32:42.700
Come on. Ferrets!

507
00:32:46.590 --> 00:32:48.100
Look's like Hasook's in trouble.

508
00:32:48.100 --> 00:32:50.390
He's in zone 3 teetering over the drink.

509
00:32:53.440 --> 00:32:54.980
And Hasook takes a dip.

510
00:32:54.980 --> 00:32:56.710
He'll be back for round two.

511
00:32:56.710 --> 00:32:59.740
Assuming the fabulous bending brothers
can hold their ground until he next round.

512
00:33:02.670 --> 00:33:08.090
Round 1 goes to the
Golden Temple Tigerdilloes!

513
00:33:08.090 --> 00:33:10.710
Come on. Hasook
get your act together!

514
00:33:15.150 --> 00:33:19.210
The Fire Ferrets are knocked into zone 2
and the Tigerdilloes advance.

515
00:33:36.320 --> 00:33:39.550
The Fire Ferrets sinch the round
in the closing seconds.

516
00:33:39.550 --> 00:33:44.580
That's one a piece. Still anyone's match
as we go into the third and final round.

517
00:33:46.210 --> 00:33:47.820
Hasook stumbles

518
00:33:47.820 --> 00:33:50.680
and now he tumbles right into his teammate.

519
00:33:50.680 --> 00:33:53.510
He and Bolin better untangle quick
if they don't want to—

520
00:33:53.510 --> 00:33:55.050
Oh too late!

521
00:33:55.950 --> 00:33:57.060
Oh no!

522
00:33:57.060 --> 00:33:59.130
It's all up to Mako now.

523
00:34:00.690 --> 00:34:02.050
he's bobbing and weaving.

524
00:34:02.050 --> 00:34:03.690
but he's not hitting back!

525
00:34:03.690 --> 00:34:06.970
If he's knocked out
the Ferrets' fabulous season is over.

526
00:34:08.460 --> 00:34:10.250
He is dancing on the edge of the ring

527
00:34:10.250 --> 00:34:12.170
withstanding the three on one barrage.

528
00:34:12.170 --> 00:34:15.640
It seems his plan is to let the Tigerdilloes
punch themselves out.

529
00:34:15.640 --> 00:34:17.380
And his plan is working.

530
00:34:17.380 --> 00:34:18.840
Han is in the pool!

531
00:34:18.840 --> 00:34:22.200
They've got nothing left in the tank
and Mako's on the offensive!

532
00:34:23.240 --> 00:34:25.140
It's two on one.

533
00:34:25.320 --> 00:34:26.810
scratch that it's one on one.

534
00:34:26.810 --> 00:34:29.440
And it's an Earth and Fire slugfest!

535
00:34:29.440 --> 00:34:34.800
There's so much smoke and dust
I can't even see where the Fire Ferret is.

536
00:34:38.210 --> 00:34:40.150
It's a knock out!

537
00:34:40.150 --> 00:34:42.650
What a win they had a hat trick folks!

538
00:34:42.650 --> 00:34:47.460
Mako pulls off the upset of the season
winning the match for the Fire Ferrets!

539
00:34:56.500 --> 00:34:57.200
Yes!

540
00:34:57.200 --> 00:35:00.490
One more win and we're in
the championship tournament!

541
00:35:01.930 --> 00:35:04.460
So. what'd ya think Korra?

542
00:35:04.460 --> 00:35:06.530
Bolin's got some moves. huh?

543
00:35:06.530 --> 00:35:09.010
What did I think?

544
00:35:09.170 --> 00:35:10.670
That was amazing!

545
00:35:10.670 --> 00:35:12.860
You did more harm than good out there.

546
00:35:12.860 --> 00:35:14.380
You almost cost us the match.

547
00:35:14.380 --> 00:35:15.870
We won didn't we?

548
00:35:15.870 --> 00:35:17.750
- Barely
- Get off my case pal.

549
00:35:19.790 --> 00:35:20.740
Useless.

550
00:35:20.740 --> 00:35:22.800
You guys were incredible out there.

551
00:35:22.800 --> 00:35:25.280
Especially you Mr. Hatrick.

552
00:35:25.280 --> 00:35:26.830
Oh you're still here…

553
00:35:26.830 --> 00:35:28.280
Oh you're still a jerk…

554
00:35:30.370 --> 00:35:31.190
anyway.

555
00:35:31.190 --> 00:35:33.220
I've been immersed in bending my whole life

556
00:35:33.220 --> 00:35:35.120
but I never learned to move like that.

557
00:35:35.120 --> 00:35:37.220
It's like there's a whole new style here.

558
00:35:37.220 --> 00:35:39.130
Think you could show me a few tricks?

559
00:35:39.130 --> 00:35:41.340
Absolutely!

560
00:35:41.340 --> 00:35:42.450
Right now?

561
00:35:42.450 --> 00:35:44.170
Come on Bolin.

562
00:35:44.170 --> 00:35:45.370
Just ignore him.

563
00:35:45.370 --> 00:35:47.600
Yeah I could show you the basics.

564
00:35:47.810 --> 00:35:50.970
I'm just not sure how my Earthbending
would translate to your Waterbending

565
00:35:51.350 --> 00:35:53.100
but we'll figure it out.

566
00:35:53.100 --> 00:35:55.150
Won't be a problem.
I'm actually an Earthbender.

567
00:35:55.150 --> 00:35:58.140
I'm sorry! No. no
I didn't mean to assume—

568
00:35:58.140 --> 00:36:01.410
I was just figuring.
with your Water Tribe get up

569
00:36:01.410 --> 00:36:04.480
that you are a Water Tribe gal.

570
00:36:04.480 --> 00:36:07.020
No you're right.
I'm a Waterbender

571
00:36:07.020 --> 00:36:09.300
and a Firebender.

572
00:36:10.510 --> 00:36:11.800
Hmm…hhmm.
I'm very confused right now.

573
00:36:11.800 --> 00:36:14.290
You're the Avatar

574
00:36:14.290 --> 00:36:15.810
and I'm an idiot.

575
00:36:15.810 --> 00:36:17.330
Both are true.

576
00:36:20.610 --> 00:36:22.210
No way… The Avatar!

577
00:36:23.150 --> 00:36:25.030
Alright. Let's see what you got.

578
00:36:29.180 --> 00:36:30.670
That was great!

579
00:36:30.670 --> 00:36:31.820
Good power!

580
00:36:31.820 --> 00:36:35.100
But in a real match you'd be a sitting turtleduck.

581
00:36:35.100 --> 00:36:36.930
Not so upright and flatfooted.

582
00:36:36.930 --> 00:36:39.480
Stay light on your toes up until the moment

583
00:36:39.480 --> 00:36:41.670
when you need to dig in and strike.

584
00:36:41.670 --> 00:36:43.660
Then—

585
00:36:46.110 --> 00:36:48.400
Okay. let me try it again.

586
00:36:52.860 --> 00:36:55.480
Wow! Nice adjustment.

587
00:36:55.480 --> 00:36:57.220
You're a natural at this!

588
00:36:57.220 --> 00:36:58.580
- Not bad.
- What's it take

589
00:36:59.180 --> 00:37:00.330
to impress this guy?

590
00:37:00.330 --> 00:37:02.410
What? I said not bad.

591
00:37:03.520 --> 00:37:05.720
You know what. it's getting late.

592
00:37:05.720 --> 00:37:08.460
I think I'm gonna turn in.
You kids have fun.

593
00:37:08.460 --> 00:37:10.920
Nice to meet you. Avatar Korra.

594
00:37:10.920 --> 00:37:13.760
Yeah. real pleasure.

595
00:37:13.760 --> 00:37:16.020
See you upstairs bro.

596
00:37:16.020 --> 00:37:17.090
Upstairs? You guys live here?

597
00:37:17.090 --> 00:37:18.770
Yeah. in the attic.

598
00:37:18.770 --> 00:37:20.020
It's nothing fancy

599
00:37:20.020 --> 00:37:21.310
but we have great views.

600
00:37:21.310 --> 00:37:23.320
But back to bending.

601
00:37:23.850 --> 00:37:25.370
Why don't you throw
that combination one more time.

602
00:37:36.480 --> 00:37:38.370
Patience Korra!

603
00:37:51.330 --> 00:37:55.490
That was a 2000-year-old historical treasure…

604
00:37:55.490 --> 00:37:57.300
what…

605
00:37:57.300 --> 00:37:58.760
what is wrong with you?!

606
00:37:58.760 --> 00:38:00.160
There's nothing wrong with me!

607
00:38:00.160 --> 00:38:02.480
I've been practicing just like you taught me!

608
00:38:02.480 --> 00:38:04.500
But it isn't sinking in okay!

609
00:38:04.500 --> 00:38:06.590
It hasn't clicked like you said it would!

610
00:38:06.590 --> 00:38:08.950
Korra this isn't something you can force.

611
00:38:08.950 --> 00:38:10.780
If you would only listen to me…

612
00:38:10.780 --> 00:38:13.100
I have been!
But you know what I think?

613
00:38:13.100 --> 00:38:14.200
Maybe the problem isn't me.

614
00:38:14.200 --> 00:38:16.410
maybe the reason
I haven't learned Airbending yet

615
00:38:16.410 --> 00:38:18.610
is because you're a terrible teacher.

616
00:38:21.020 --> 00:38:23.110
Yeah you're a terrible teacher. Daddy!

617
00:38:36.100 --> 00:38:37.780
Okay!

618
00:38:37.780 --> 00:38:38.870
Everyone here?

619
00:38:38.870 --> 00:38:39.970
Wait…

620
00:38:39.970 --> 00:38:41.400
where's Korra?

621
00:38:41.400 --> 00:38:43.920
Honestly Pema.
I am at my wit's end with that girl.

622
00:38:43.920 --> 00:38:45.790
I don't know how to get through to her.

623
00:38:45.790 --> 00:38:50.450
The best thing you can do right now

624
00:38:50.450 --> 00:38:52.400
is give Korra some space.

625
00:38:52.400 --> 00:38:55.690
You must promise me that
your teenage years won't be like this.

626
00:38:55.690 --> 00:38:59.170
I will make no such promises.

627
00:39:05.790 --> 00:39:08.330
I didn't miss your match did I?

628
00:39:08.330 --> 00:39:10.130
You guys look like you lost already.

629
00:39:10.130 --> 00:39:12.940
- We might as well have.
- Hasook's a no good no show.

630
00:39:13.970 --> 00:39:16.190
You got two minutes
to come out ready to play

631
00:39:16.190 --> 00:39:17.850
or you're disqualified.

632
00:39:17.850 --> 00:39:20.290
Well there goes our shot
at the tournament

633
00:39:20.290 --> 00:39:22.220
and the winnings.

634
00:39:22.220 --> 00:39:23.980
Couldn't you ask one of those guys to fill in?

635
00:39:23.980 --> 00:39:27.010
Nah. the rules say you can only compete on one team.

636
00:39:27.010 --> 00:39:29.690
Well then…what about me?

637
00:39:29.690 --> 00:39:31.410
I'm a topnotch Waterbender

638
00:39:31.410 --> 00:39:32.850
if I do say so myself.

639
00:39:32.850 --> 00:39:34.790
But you're the Avatar…

640
00:39:34.790 --> 00:39:36.160
isn't that cheating?

641
00:39:36.160 --> 00:39:38.040
It isn't cheating if
I only do Waterbending.

642
00:39:38.040 --> 00:39:39.860
No way.
I'd rather forfeit

643
00:39:39.860 --> 00:39:41.370
than look like a fool out there.

644
00:39:41.500 --> 00:39:42.130
Wow

645
00:39:42.130 --> 00:39:44.260
thanks for the vote of confidence…

646
00:39:44.260 --> 00:39:45.730
Time's up
you in or out?

647
00:39:45.730 --> 00:39:46.530
- We're in.
- We are?

648
00:39:46.530 --> 00:39:48.610
- Yes!
- Hey. I didn't agree to this!

649
00:39:50.120 --> 00:39:50.120
You can thank me later.

650
00:39:50.120 --> 00:39:51.910
This girl is crazy…

651
00:39:51.910 --> 00:39:53.480
Looks like the Fire Ferrets

652
00:39:53.480 --> 00:39:56.750
have ferreted out a
last minute replacement Waterbender.

653
00:39:56.750 --> 00:39:58.390
Let's see if she's another
diamond in the rough

654
00:39:58.390 --> 00:40:00.090
like the brothers
from the school of hard knocks.

655
00:40:01.270 --> 00:40:03.730
Don't do anything too fancy
or aggressive.

656
00:40:03.730 --> 00:40:05.390
In fact. don't do anything.

657
00:40:05.390 --> 00:40:07.480
Just try not to get knocked
off the ring.

658
00:40:07.480 --> 00:40:09.110
You got it captain.

659
00:40:10.710 --> 00:40:11.820
Players

660
00:40:11.820 --> 00:40:13.020
are you ready?

661
00:40:20.030 --> 00:40:21.890
Whoo! Man overboard!

662
00:40:22.940 --> 00:40:24.010
Fire Ferret Waterbender penalty.

663
00:40:24.340 --> 00:40:25.810
move back one zone.

664
00:40:25.810 --> 00:40:27.670
What? Why?

665
00:40:27.670 --> 00:40:30.220
You're only allowed to
knock players off the back of the ring.

666
00:40:30.220 --> 00:40:31.760
not over the sides.

667
00:40:32.710 --> 00:40:34.040
Oh…whoops.

668
00:40:35.640 --> 00:40:37.230
And we're back in action

669
00:40:37.230 --> 00:40:41.230
after that hiccup. But I'm not so sure
this replacement player knows what she's doing.

670
00:40:43.050 --> 00:40:44.000
Fowl! Over the line!

671
00:40:44.000 --> 00:40:45.660
Move back to zone three.

672
00:40:45.660 --> 00:40:48.100
Ugh! I'll show you over the line.

673
00:40:51.210 --> 00:40:54.290
The Platypus Bears take round 1.

674
00:40:55.220 --> 00:40:58.040
The Platypus Bears know a green player
when they see one

675
00:40:58.040 --> 00:41:01.470
and they are focusing the brunt
of their bending on this poor girl.

676
00:41:04.920 --> 00:41:06.020
What a minute.

677
00:41:06.020 --> 00:41:08.090
did that Waterbender just Earthbend?

678
00:41:10.010 --> 00:41:11.580
Fowl!

679
00:41:11.580 --> 00:41:13.100
I think.

680
00:41:15.860 --> 00:41:17.270
Did I see that right?

681
00:41:17.270 --> 00:41:20.990
Hold on folks we're just waiting
for the Referee's official call

682
00:41:20.990 --> 00:41:23.780
but I think this replacement player could be…

683
00:41:23.780 --> 00:41:25.620
Pardon me everyone. has anyone seen Korra this evening?

684
00:41:25.620 --> 00:41:27.090
She's not in her room.

685
00:41:27.090 --> 00:41:28.600
You've gotta be kidding me!

686
00:41:28.600 --> 00:41:30.740
She's the Avatar. folks

687
00:41:30.740 --> 00:41:32.650
playing in a Pro-Bending match!

688
00:41:32.650 --> 00:41:34.300
Can you believe that?

689
00:41:34.300 --> 00:41:35.710
I'll get her myself!

690
00:41:38.260 --> 00:41:41.030
The Avatar will be permitted to continue

691
00:41:41.030 --> 00:41:43.430
so long as she solely bends water.

692
00:41:47.730 --> 00:41:51.120
This girl may be the Avatar but she's no Pro-Bender

693
00:41:51.120 --> 00:41:53.660
and the Platypus Bears are intent
on exploiting that weakness.

694
00:41:53.660 --> 00:41:56.080
They're giving her their best

695
00:41:56.080 --> 00:41:57.910
and her best is not enough to stop it.

696
00:41:58.110 --> 00:41:59.460
Aaaaaannd...-

697
00:41:59.460 --> 00:42:00.470
she's in the drink.

698
00:42:07.690 --> 00:42:10.170
Oh hey Tenzin…

699
00:42:10.170 --> 00:42:13.000
I thought you didn't like
coming to these matches.

700
00:42:14.480 --> 00:42:17.150
Once again you have
flagrantly disobeyed my orders.

701
00:42:17.150 --> 00:42:18.910
You were to stay on the island.

702
00:42:18.910 --> 00:42:19.910
Let's go.

703
00:42:19.910 --> 00:42:20.650
No!

704
00:42:20.650 --> 00:42:22.480
I'm kind of in the middle of something.

705
00:42:22.480 --> 00:42:24.560
I have tried my very best to get through to you

706
00:42:24.560 --> 00:42:26.410
by being gentle and patient

707
00:42:26.410 --> 00:42:29.440
But clearly the only thing
you respond to is force.

708
00:42:29.440 --> 00:42:32.400
So I am ordering you to come back to the temple.
Right now!

709
00:42:32.400 --> 00:42:36.860
Why? So I can sit around and meditate about how bad I am at Airbending?

710
00:42:36.860 --> 00:42:40.420
You know I'm beginning to think
there's a reason I haven't been able to learn it.

711
00:42:40.420 --> 00:42:42.580
because maybe I don't even need!

712
00:42:42.580 --> 00:42:43.760
What?

713
00:42:43.760 --> 00:42:45.510
That is a ludicrous suggestion!

714
00:42:45.510 --> 00:42:48.880
The Avatar needs to learn Airbending.
it is not optional!

715
00:42:48.880 --> 00:42:51.420
No. THIS is what I need to learn!

716
00:42:51.420 --> 00:42:53.120
Modern styles of fighting!

717
00:42:53.120 --> 00:42:55.790
Being Avatar isn't all about fighting. Korra!

718
00:42:55.790 --> 00:42:57.690
When will you learn that?

719
00:42:57.690 --> 00:42:59.380
I have a match to go finish.

720
00:43:00.300 --> 00:43:03.870
The Platypus Bears win round 2!

721
00:43:03.870 --> 00:43:04.020
Round 3!
The Platypus Bears win round 2!

722
00:43:04.020 --> 00:43:06.480
Round 3!

723
00:43:11.190 --> 00:43:15.170
The Platypus Bears come out of the gate
and quickly go after the Ferret brothers.

724
00:43:15.170 --> 00:43:20.210
They're corralled in the corner. wedged in the edge of zone 1
unable to come to the Avatar's rescue

725
00:43:20.210 --> 00:43:22.060
and boy does she need it.

726
00:43:27.790 --> 00:43:31.630
Looks like the Avatar's Pro-Bending
debut is gonna be cut short

727
00:43:31.850 --> 00:43:35.540
as she's pushed back to zone 3
and the water is calling her name.

728
00:43:35.540 --> 00:43:37.800
It's only a matter of time before—

729
00:43:37.800 --> 00:43:41.520
Hold the phone. stop the presses!
She's still in the game folks!

730
00:43:41.520 --> 00:43:43.600
And she's moving like an
entirely different player!

731
00:43:43.600 --> 00:43:47.670
Suddenly all of the Platypus Bear
strikes are only striking air.

732
00:43:49.350 --> 00:43:50.900
Well how about that…

733
00:43:53.190 --> 00:43:55.240
The Platypus Bears have no juice left

734
00:43:55.240 --> 00:43:57.620
but Mako and Bolin are still fresh and juicy.

735
00:44:22.130 --> 00:44:23.040
Knockout!

736
00:44:23.040 --> 00:44:27.690
The Fire Ferrets come from
way behind and steal the win!

737
00:44:27.910 --> 00:44:30.760
What an upset folks!
The rookies. Avatar in tow.

738
00:44:30.760 --> 00:44:33.050
have nabbed a place in
the championship tournament!

739
00:44:33.050 --> 00:44:35.460
I cannot believe it!

740
00:44:40.510 --> 00:44:42.280
Korra. what can I say?

741
00:44:42.280 --> 00:44:45.040
You really came alive in that last round.

742
00:44:45.040 --> 00:44:47.050
The way you dodged their attacks…

743
00:44:47.050 --> 00:44:48.470
you are a natural.

744
00:44:48.470 --> 00:44:49.500
Thanks

745
00:44:49.500 --> 00:44:51.050
but I can't take all the credit.

746
00:44:51.050 --> 00:44:52.960
someone else taught me those moves.

747
00:45:01.090 --> 00:45:02.800
I'm really sorry

748
00:45:02.800 --> 00:45:05.000
about everything I said.

749
00:45:05.000 --> 00:45:07.160
I was really frustrated with myself and

750
00:45:07.160 --> 00:45:08.920
I took it out on you.

751
00:45:08.920 --> 00:45:11.170
I think I owe an apology too.

752
00:45:11.170 --> 00:45:13.510
I was trying to teach you about patience

753
00:45:13.510 --> 00:45:15.210
and I lost mine.

754
00:45:15.210 --> 00:45:16.860
No hard feelings?

755
00:45:16.860 --> 00:45:17.860
Of course not.

756
00:45:17.870 --> 00:45:20.550
By the way you were really
good out there tonight.

757
00:45:20.550 --> 00:45:22.830
You moved like an Airbender.

758
00:45:22.830 --> 00:45:25.250
You stayed and watched?

759
00:45:25.250 --> 00:45:29.290
I did. Pro-Bending turned out to be
the perfect teaching tool for you.

760
00:45:32.910 --> 00:45:35.660
I'll see you tomorrow for
Airbending practice bright and early!

761
00:45:35.660 --> 00:45:39.070
And by the way I kinda
permanently joined the Fire Ferrets

762
00:45:39.070 --> 00:45:40.760
and we're playing in the tournament
in a couple of weeks!

763
00:46:06.030 --> 00:46:08.900
Original sub by:
Scarlett
www.addic7ed.com

764
00:46:08.900 --> 00:46:10.900
Sync by:
HerrySis
